set default deny

interface mgmt = "ens3"
interface wan = "wan0"
interface dmz = "dmz0"
interface app = "app0"

table <admin> { 198.51.100.10, 203.0.113.0/24 }
table <edge_nodes> { 10.30.0.10, 10.30.0.11 }
table <app_nodes> { 10.40.0.10, 10.40.0.11 }
table <blocked_sources> { 192.0.2.66, 192.0.2.67 }

queue public on wan bandwidth 150mbit
queue admin on wan bandwidth 10mbit parent public

pass in on mgmt proto tcp from any to any port 22 keep state
pass out on mgmt from any to any keep state

rdr on wan proto tcp from any to any port 80 -> 10.30.0.10 port 8080
rdr on wan proto tcp from any to any port 443 -> 10.30.0.10 port 8443

block in log (all) on wan from <blocked_sources> to any
pass in log on wan proto tcp from any to any port 80 queue public keep state
pass in log on wan proto tcp from any to any port 443 queue public keep state
pass in log (user) on wan proto tcp from <admin> to any port 22 queue admin keep state

pass in on dmz proto tcp from <edge_nodes> to <app_nodes> port 8080 keep state queue public
pass in on dmz proto tcp from <edge_nodes> to <app_nodes> port 8443 keep state queue public
pass out on app proto tcp from <app_nodes> to any port 443 keep state queue public

block in log (all) on wan from any to any
block in log (all) on dmz from any to any
block out log (user) on wan from any to any
